7.71	Firewalker_(The_X-Files)	Firewalker (The X-Files)	"Firewalker" is the ninth episode of the second season of the American science fiction television series The X-Files. It premiered on the Fox network on . It was written by Howard Gordon, directed by David Nutter, and featured guest appearances by Bradley Whitford, Leland Orser and Shawnee Smith. The episode is a "Monster-of-the-Week" story, unconnected to the series' wider mythology.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/8/81/Firewalker_TXF.jpg
